### HTML (index.html)
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Checkout</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="checkout-container">
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Your Checkout Summary</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Cart Items Section -->
    <div id="cart-items">
        <ul>
            <li>
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Product Image">
                <div class="product-details">
                    <p class="product-name">Sample Product 1</p>
                    <p class="price">$9.99</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <!-- Add more products here -->
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Shipping Information Section -->
    <div id="shipping-info">
        <h3>Shipping Information</h3>
        <form>
            <label for="name">Name:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name"><br>
            <label for="address">Address:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="address" name="address"><br>
            <label for="city">City:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="city" name="city"><br>
            <label for="state">State/Province:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="state" name="state"><br>
            <label for="zip">ZIP Code:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="zip" name="zip"><br>
            <label for="country">Country:</label><br>
            <select id="country">
                <option value="US">United States</option>
                <option value="CA">Canada</option>
            </select><br>
        </form>
    </div>

    <!-- Review Section -->
    <div id="review-section">
        <h3>Review and Confirm</h3>
        <p>Total: $19.98</p>
        <button disabled class="pay-now-btn">Pay Now</button>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
```

### CSS (styles.css)
```css
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body, html {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    height: 100%;
}

.checkout-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

.header h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #333;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding-bottom: .5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

#cart-items ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 0;
}

#cart-items li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
}

.product-details {
    margin-left: .5rem;
}

.product-name, .price {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
}

.price {
    color: red;
    font-weight: bold;
}

#shipping-info form label {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

#shipping-info form input, #shipping-info form select {
    width: calc(100% - 24px);
    padding: .5rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 1rem;
}

#review-section h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

#review-section p {
    color: #333;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
}

button.pay-now-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: .8rem;
    background-color: #FF69B4;
    border: none;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background-color .3s ease, opacity .3s ease;
}

button.pay-now-btn:hover {
    background-color: #cc5588;
}
```

### JavaScript (optional - just for placeholder functionality)
```html
<script>
document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
    document.getElementById('name').placeholder = "John Doe";
    document.getElementById('address').placeholder = "123 Main St";
    document.getElementById('city').placeholder = "Anytown";
    document.getElementById('state').placeholder = "CA";
    document.getElementById('zip').placeholder = "90210";
});
</script>
```

### Explanation
- **HTML**: The structure includes a header, cart items section, shipping information form, and review/confirmation section.
- **CSS**: Styles are designed to mimic Shopify's checkout page layout with appropriate padding, borders, font styles, etc.
- **JavaScript (Optional)**: Adds placeholder text to the input fields for better visual representation.

This setup should give you a static but visually similar Shopify-like checkout page. You can further customize the CSS and HTML as needed to match your specific requirements.

